{"tid":2083403,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳宣儀久違韓文問候「我回來了」！　釣出多榮留言…粉絲興奮：要回宇宙少女了嗎？","createTime":"2020-06-28T16:59:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T01:24:13.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9978d9e997561453cdad60448b90726b229f3d07","tid":2083403,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:59:20.000Z","msg":"南韓女團宇宙少女的大陸成員孟美岐、吳宣儀於2018年回歸練習生身份，參加了選秀節目《創造101》，分別拿下了第1、2名的好成績，成功以「火箭少女101」成員再出道，日前結束了2年的合約，引起外界好奇兩人未來的動向。吳宣儀28日睽違多時更新了IG，內文讓不少粉絲相當興奮問道「要回宇宙少女了嗎？」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4968/d4968227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4968%2Fd4968227.jpg&h=cb833f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲吳宣儀以火箭少女，在大陸活躍活動了2年。（圖／翻攝吳宣儀IG）<br />\n<br />\n吳宣儀28日在IG曬出多張自拍照，並於內文用韓文寫下「我回來了」（안녕, 돌아온당），底下引來成員多榮特地用中文回覆道「我想你」，此舉引來不少網友猜測她在預告即將回歸宇宙少女，進行團體活動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4968/d4968225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4968%2Fd4968225.jpg&h=89a63802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲吳宣儀貼文吸引了多榮回應。（圖／翻攝吳宣儀IG）<br />\n<br />\n貼文底下網友紛紛留言說道「真的要回來了嗎」、「期待回宇宙少女合體！」、「好想妳呀」、「好期待13個人的舞台」，而由於吳宣儀已經將近半年未更新IG，也有人認為「只是找回IG密碼，說回來了而已吧」。<br />\n<br />\n孟美岐、吳宣儀在以「火箭少女101」成員活動的期間，在大陸收穫極高的人氣，如今合約結束，團體解散，由於包含程瀟在內的3名大陸成員，雖同屬宇宙少女，而經紀約卻是屬於樂華娛樂，而非STARSHIP，因此之後是否回歸南韓進行宇宙少女的活動，是外界關注的焦點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4968/d4968224.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4968%2Fd4968224.jpg&h=450c389c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲程瀟、孟美岐、吳宣儀近2年演藝重心都在大陸。（圖／翻攝IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />竟然用韓文"},{"pid":"d54c75ce176432d1e295a3d5d4e6ba31073e050d","tid":2083403,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:02:08.000Z","msg":"帶著肺炎CB嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n程瀟一個大奶妹就夠了"},{"pid":"9868b204d40d53b93cf7114133b7bfe362986ebd","tid":2083403,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:06:04.000Z","msg":"嘔心"},{"pid":"2d98ad8fba518eeb642f52b8f8b4682f26f3e9bc","tid":2083403,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d54c75ce176432d1e295a3d5d4e6ba31073e050d","tid":2083403,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:02:08.000Z","msg":"帶著肺炎CB嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n程瀟一個大奶妹就夠了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"5G重656講韓文"},{"pid":"1f9b56abea05f1bdc4f38514afcd78dcd0b09692","tid":2083403,"uid":68678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:09:21.000Z","msg":"又有多隊嘢反"},{"pid":"22f6f32aaf0501c0552efbd826798d9822e729b2","tid":2083403,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:13:06.000Z","msg":"好似仲正過韓國成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c831c5a8008ee4c5a2452dcdd4aa565a909b566","tid":2083403,"uid":74065,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"22f6f32aaf0501c0552efbd826798d9822e729b2","tid":2083403,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:13:06.000Z","msg":"好似仲正過韓國成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:14:15.000Z","msg":"望下你個名就知你眼疾色盲白內障失明失聰"},{"pid":"91b3bbd52b28bae7c0c867ff3594c4f8019c3c55","tid":2083403,"uid":124252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22f6f32aaf0501c0552efbd826798d9822e729b2","tid":2083403,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:13:06.000Z"